data.name: ReadPaParticipantAddress
data.value: select top(1) T1.TYPE, T1.STREET1, T1.STREET2, T1.CITY, T1.[STATE], T1.ZIP, T1.ZIP4, T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.PRP_IDENTIFIER, T1.PAF_TYPE, T1.PRE_NUMBER, T1.PAF_TSTAMP from CKT_PA_REFER_PART T2 join CKT_PA_PART_ADDR T1 on (T2.PAF_TSTAMP = T1.PAF_TSTAMP) and (T2.PRE_NUMBER = T1.PRE_NUMBER) and (T2.PAF_TYPE = T1.PAF_TYPE) and (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.PRP_IDENTIFIER) and (@pafTstamp = T2.PAF_TSTAMP) and (@preNumber = T2.PRE_NUMBER) and (@pafType = T2.PAF_TYPE) and (T2.RELATIONSHIP = 'AP') and (T1.TYPE = 'E')
